TEXT 968 -8 Left 2 ;Notes:\n1) Output high only for VL < Vin < Vh\n2) VL = Vcc * R3/(R1+ R2 + R3) = 4V\n3) Vh = Vcc * (R2+R3)/(R1+ R2 + R3) = 8V\n4) U1 and U2 should be open collector comparators and R4 should be connected to Vcc instead of GND,
